Fourth Department,

February, 1982

(February 26, 1982) Kevin D. Cox, Erie County Public Administrator, as Administrator of the Estate of James Watts, Jr., Deceased, Respondent, v County of Erie, Appellant.

Appeal dismissed, without costs, upon stipulation. (Appeal from order of Supreme Court, Erie County, Cook, J. — summary judgment.) Present — Simons, J. P., Hancock, Jr., Denman, Moule and Schnepp, JJ.
